        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks JM for present of McClintock’s work [Sir Francis Leopold McClintock, <hi rend="italic">The voyage of the "Fox" in the Arctic seas</hi> (1859)], which he and his wife look forward to reading.</p>  
<p>Asks to be told when reprint [of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>] is ready.</p> 
        </abstract>
